10
00:01:34,120 --> 00:01:36,390
<b>Tonight, you will die.</b>

11
00:01:37,460 --> 00:01:39,860
<b>- What? - That's all I know.</b>

12
00:01:40,590 --> 00:01:42,130
<b>My memories aren't completely intact.</b>

13
00:01:44,330 --> 00:01:47,070
<b>All I know is that, just like me, you've become the kid's target.</b>

14
00:01:47,970 --> 00:01:49,070
<b>What kid?</b>

15
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:51,100
<b>The young devil.</b>

16
00:01:55,340 --> 00:01:57,410
<b>- Who are you? - He's young but evil.</b>

17
00:01:59,280 --> 00:02:01,980
<b>I only cooperated to protect my daughter.</b>

18
00:02:03,620 --> 00:02:06,420
<b>Although, even these memories will soon be erased.</b>

19
00:02:08,090 --> 00:02:10,560
<b>Let's go. Let me loose...</b>

20
00:02:10,860 --> 00:02:12,260
<b>- and we'll find a way. - Quiet.</b>

21
00:02:19,870 --> 00:02:21,030
<b>He's here.</b>

22
00:02:29,810 --> 00:02:31,410
<b>Don't underestimate him...</b>

23
00:02:32,510 --> 00:02:34,080
<b>or you'll die a gruesome death.</b>

24
00:02:42,420 --> 00:02:44,020
<b>What did you do to Sang Ah?</b>

25
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:47,030
<b>But I did everything you asked.</b>

26
00:02:48,860 --> 00:02:50,300
<b>I'll kill you!</b>

27
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:05,480
<b>There is going to be a party?</b>

28
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:07,610
<b>Unbelievable...</b>

29
00:03:17,360 --> 00:03:18,490
<b>Who are you?</b>

30
00:04:16,850 --> 00:04:17,920
<b>What...</b>

31
00:04:51,520 --> 00:04:53,720
<b>Kid. Hey, kid?</b>

32
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:26,620
<b>Are you all right?</b>

33
00:05:32,330 --> 00:05:33,460
<b>Kid!</b>

34
00:05:34,790 --> 00:05:35,930
<b>Hey, kid. Are you all right?</b>

35
00:06:14,070 --> 00:06:15,200
<b>It was you.</b>

36
00:06:16,770 --> 00:06:17,940
<b>You liar.</b>

37
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:22,180
<b>You were the one who killed seven people in Shimbae...</b>

38
00:06:23,340 --> 00:06:24,740
<b>20 years ago.</b>

39
00:06:27,080 --> 00:06:29,520
<b>No. No.</b>

40
00:06:29,950 --> 00:06:33,320
<b>No! No, that can't be!</b>

41
00:06:39,060 --> 00:06:41,600
<b>You're the Eraser who killed...</b>

42
00:06:45,870 --> 00:06:47,030
<b>all those people.</b>

43
00:07:11,990 --> 00:07:13,160
<b>Where's your proof?</b>

44
00:07:18,870 --> 00:07:20,900
<b>All the people he loathed...</b>

45
00:07:21,670 --> 00:07:23,370
<b>fell victim to the Eraser.</b>

46
00:07:24,540 --> 00:07:25,810
<b>Park Ki Dan,</b>

47
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:28,980
<b>Oh Yeon Tak,</b>

48
00:07:29,810 --> 00:07:30,910
<b>Jo Sung Dong...</b>

49
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,810
<b>No.</b>

50
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:39,590
