64
00:08:23,030 --> 00:08:24,030
<b>Why do you ask?</b>

65
00:08:24,900 --> 00:08:26,070
<b>To add another name to your list of victims?</b>

66
00:08:27,070 --> 00:08:28,670
<b>I'll just scan your memory myself.</b>

67
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,940
<b>- Freeze! - Freeze.</b>

68
00:08:32,810 --> 00:08:34,410
<b>- Arrest him. - Lower your weapons.</b>

69
00:08:34,640 --> 00:08:35,640
<b>We're here to investigate...</b>

70
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:36,740
<b>Deputy Chief Lee's alleged corruption.</b>

71
00:08:36,740 --> 00:08:37,840
