79
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:23,660
<b>How dare someone like you question my conduct?</b>

80
00:09:25,230 --> 00:09:28,400
<b>You foolish girl.</b>

81
00:09:29,160 --> 00:09:31,130
<b>You couldn't see the murderer in front of you...</b>

82
00:09:31,230 --> 00:09:32,500
<b>even with the hint I handed over.</b>

83
00:09:33,200 --> 00:09:35,240
<b>This is your job now.</b>

84
00:09:35,570 --> 00:09:38,570
<b>It's up to you to fill in the blanks.</b>

85
00:09:38,570 --> 00:09:41,470
<b>Actually, I figured it out a long time ago.</b>

86
00:09:41,910 --> 00:09:44,640
<b>The relationship between Detective Dong and the victims...</b>

87
00:09:44,740 --> 00:09:47,780
<b>and how you tried to get rid of him without making the move yourself.</b>

88
00:09:50,150 --> 00:09:52,990
<b>What I couldn't figure out was the motive. But now I know.</b>

89
00:09:54,420 --> 00:09:56,090
<b>It was to hide your own crimes.</b>

90
00:10:11,770 --> 00:10:14,010
<b>You kept silent even when you knew he was the killer?</b>

91
00:10:14,370 --> 00:10:15,880
<b>Where's your evidence?</b>

92
00:10:15,880 --> 00:10:18,550
<b>Only Dong Baek's enemies were murdered.</b>

93
00:10:18,550 --> 00:10:21,610
<b>At the very least, Dong Baek is the Eraser's accomplice.</b>

94
00:10:21,610 --> 00:10:22,620
<b>What about Chun Ki Soo's son...</b>

95
00:10:22,620 --> 00:10:24,050
<b>- and the firefighter? - Them too!</b>

96
00:10:24,420 --> 00:10:25,990
<b>Dong Baek's taking revenge...</b>

97
00:10:25,990 --> 00:10:27,590
<b>on what happened in Shimbae 20 years ago.</b>

98
00:10:27,690 --> 00:10:30,120
