<b>My son's inside.</b>

149
00:14:33,700 --> 00:14:35,000
<b>Joon Young!</b>

150
00:14:36,970 --> 00:14:39,440
<b>Move my family to a safe house.</b>

151
00:14:39,670 --> 00:14:40,740
<b>Excuse me?</b>

152
00:14:42,610 --> 00:14:44,680
<b>Get the NIS, the Secret Service, everyone,</b>

153
00:14:44,710 --> 00:14:48,110
<b>and evacuate my wife and son immediately.</b>

154
00:14:48,350 --> 00:14:49,720
<b>Yes, sir.</b>

155
00:14:59,820 --> 00:15:02,650
<b>Dong Baek fled last night.</b>

156
00:15:02,690 --> 00:15:05,050
<b>That is all we have on the case.</b>

157
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:08,020
<b>From this moment forth, Dong Baek is our prime suspect.</b>

158
00:15:08,020 --> 00:15:10,030
<b>Concentrate all our forces on arresting him.</b>

159
00:15:10,160 --> 00:15:12,060
<b>We will also locate and monitor those who may help Dong Baek.</b>

160
00:15:12,060 --> 00:15:13,130
