161
00:15:13,130 --> 00:15:17,670
<b>Captain Koo Kyung Tan, and Officer Oh Se Hoon.</b>

162
00:15:17,670 --> 00:15:20,240
<b>It's bad enough Superintendent Han was suspended,</b>

163
00:15:20,240 --> 00:15:21,470
