164
00:15:21,470 --> 00:15:23,910
<b>Dong Baek? The Eraser's accomplice? You know what he's like.</b>

165
00:15:23,910 --> 00:15:25,610
<b>He loathes murderers with a passion.</b>

166
00:15:25,610 --> 00:15:28,180
<b>- Hey. Am I right or not? - It's true.</b>

167
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:29,980
<b>It's understandable to suspect him.</b>

168
00:15:31,050 --> 00:15:32,080
<b>What was that, punk?</b>

169
00:15:33,220 --> 00:15:36,590
<b>Who would instruct you to give us such an order without any evidence?</b>

170
00:15:36,590 --> 00:15:38,190
<b>If he resists arrest,</b>

171
00:15:38,660 --> 00:15:40,890
<b>you may use any and all necessary force.</b>

172
00:15:41,460 --> 00:15:42,860
<b>Even guns?</b>

173
00:15:43,860 --> 00:15:46,760
<b>Sir. Whose order is this?</b>

174
00:15:46,960 --> 00:15:49,600
<b>Even those ignorant prosecutors can't give an order like that.</b>

175
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:52,440
<b>Dong Baek is a hothead, so he'd never come readily,</b>

176
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:53,670
<b>but you want us to shoot him?</b>

177
00:15:53,800 --> 00:15:56,670
<b>You know his temper. This is an order to kill.</b>

178
00:15:57,010 --> 00:15:59,510
<b>- Am I right or not? - You're right.</b>

179
00:16:03,110 --> 00:16:07,680
<b>(Byun Young Soo)</b>

180
00:16:10,550 --> 00:16:11,990
<b>Please show me the evidence.</b>

181
00:16:15,930 --> 00:16:19,260
<b>Hey, you. Young Soo. Are you defying an order?</b>

182
00:16:19,260 --> 00:16:21,030
<b>It's not defiance. I'm requesting evidence.</b>

183
00:16:21,030 --> 00:16:24,000
<b>The prosecutor's arrest warrant wasn't a request for cooperation.</b>

184
00:16:25,740 --> 00:16:28,500
<b>Your job is to catch him before the prosecutors and find evidence.</b>

185
00:16:28,500 --> 00:16:29,610
<b>Don't be a rude punk...</b>

186
00:16:30,170 --> 00:16:32,110
<b>and demand evidence, you jerk!</b>

187
