<b>What's with the rain?</b>

193
00:17:27,030 --> 00:17:29,830
<b>It looks like it'll pass. Did you find Moon Yong Gang?</b>

194
00:17:29,970 --> 00:17:32,540
<b>He disappeared without a trace. What about Chun Ki Soo?</b>

195
00:17:32,540 --> 00:17:34,400
<b>He hid himself well.</b>

196
00:17:35,400 --> 00:17:36,440
<b>What do we do?</b>

197
00:17:36,540 --> 00:17:40,210
<b>I'll do as Superintendent Han said and stay with Assemblyman Bang.</b>

198
00:17:40,210 --> 00:17:42,850
<b>You keep trying to locate Moon Yong Gang.</b>

199
00:17:42,850 --> 00:17:45,010
<b>I don't know where to start.</b>

200
00:17:45,380 --> 00:17:47,350
<b>We don't have time. Look at this.</b>

201
00:17:47,650 --> 00:17:50,750
<b>Every news agency is bent on catching Baek.</b>

202
00:17:50,750 --> 00:17:52,090
<b>(Despicable Serial Killer Suspect Dong Baek, Did He Fool the Nation?)</b>

203
00:17:52,090 --> 00:17:54,190
<b>This is the agency where Kang Ji Eun works.</b>

204
00:17:54,590 --> 00:17:57,060
<b>No one in media is on Baek's side.</b>

205
00:17:57,530 --> 00:18:00,300
<b>We're the only ones on his side, so stay on top of your game.</b>

206
00:18:00,760 --> 00:18:02,700
<b>I'm going to meet with Ms. Kang.</b>

207
00:18:02,700 --> 00:18:05,970
<b>For what? She's powerless.</b>

208
00:18:06,040 --> 00:18:07,140
<b>I'll call you.</b>

209
00:18:07,840 --> 00:18:09,040
<b>Se Hoon.</b>

210
00:19:40,460 --> 00:19:41,530
<b>So you're alive.</b>

211
00:19:45,940 --> 00:19:47,440
<b>How did you know I was here?</b>

212
00:19:48,370 --> 00:19:49,440
<b>Sit.</b>

213
00:19:51,870 --> 00:19:53,480
<b>This feels like an interrogation.</b>

214
00:19:54,110 --> 00:19:55,310
<b>Because I'm going to interrogate you.</b>

215
00:19:57,510 --> 00:19:58,580
<b>About what?</b>

216
00:19:58,750 --> 00:20:00,180
<b>The truth about you.</b>

217
00:20:01,750 --> 00:20:04,050
<b>You're interrogating me from a murderer's desk.</b>

218
00:20:06,160 --> 00:20:09,030
<b>Why? In case I'm the Eraser?</b>

219
00:20:09,590 --> 00:20:10,660
<b>That too.</b>

220
00:20:10,660 --> 00:20:14,630
<b>If I'm really the murderer, your life is in my hands.</b>

221
00:20:14,630 --> 00:20:17,600
<b>I told you. The moment I die,</b>

222
00:20:17,830 --> 00:20:19,900
<b>this will record everything and send the file to my colleagues.</b>

223
00:20:21,370 --> 00:20:22,470
<b>Shall we begin?</b>

224
00:20:26,940 --> 00:20:27,980
<b>You'd better be nervous.</b>

